      <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 align-items-md-center g-5 py-5">
        <div class="col d-flex flex-column align-items-start gap-2">
          <h2 class="fw-bold text-body-emphasis">Feeling indecisive?</h2>
          <p class="text-body-secondary">We've got you covered. choice. is the ultimate decision-making web app designed for those moments when you just can't choose. Whether it's a simple coin flip, a quick game of rock-paper-scissors, or a randomized option picker, we take the stress out of choosing so you can move forward with confidence.</p>
        </div>
  
